{"lemma":"مَجْهُول","slug":"مَجْهُول","root":"ج.ه.ل","root_slug":"ج-ه-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ه-ل","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6593"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%92%D9%87%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%84"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"unknown"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"anonymous"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"passive voice"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a variety of date palm with large and sweet fruit"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of جَهِلَ (jahila, “to be ignorant, to not know”), from the root ج ه ل (j h l): literally, “not known”. The word is used to describe the passive voice, because in the passive the agent of the verb is usually not mentioned and is therefore unknown."},"ipa":["/mad͡ʒ.huːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6593","headword_ar":"مَجْهُولٌ","root":"jahila","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unknown"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakibotu AlmafaAzapN","text_ar":"رَكِبْتُ المَفَازَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY majohuwlihaA","text_ar":"عَلَى مَجْهُولِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I ventured upon traversing the desert notwithstanding its unknown character"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) ―         -b2-  [A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of unknown origin."},{"kind":"text","text":"A book"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of unknown authorship."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b3-  In grammar, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passive voice."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN majohuwlapN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ مَجْهُولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel that has never been milked:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has no brand upon her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a she-camel that has never conceived."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]}}